# Faisal Haroon Brand Theme

This document defines the color palette, gradients, shadows, and typography to be used across all creative outputs (social media, thumbnails, banners, posts, reels, story covers, and motion graphics).

## Core Palette (HEX)
- Primary Blue: #00A8FF
- Secondary Cyan: #00E5FF
- Neon Accent: #0066FF
- Background: #000000
- Foreground/Text: #FFFFFF
- Subtle Grid Line (overlay): rgba(0, 168, 255, 0.03)

## Gradients
- Primary Gradient (CTA / Bars / Underlines):
  - Direction: left → right
  - From: #00A8FF
  - To:   #00E5FF
  - CSS example: `linear-gradient(90deg, #00A8FF 0%, #00E5FF 100%)`

- Accent Gradient (Background glow spots):
  - Use low-opacity radial glows with blues
  - Examples: `rgba(0, 100, 255, 0.06)`, `rgba(0, 150, 255, 0.06)`

## Glow & Shadow Styles
- Soft Outer Glow: 0 0 24px rgba(0, 168, 255, 0.45)
- Subtle Card Shadow: 0 2px 42px rgba(0, 229, 255, 0.08–0.15)
- Divider/Border (glow style):
  - Border: 1px solid rgba(0, 168, 255, 0.30–0.40)
  - Inner Glow: inset 0 0 20px rgba(0, 168, 255, 0.10)

## Typography
- Display/Headings: Orbitron (Google Fonts)
  - Fallbacks: sans-serif
  - Usage: H1–H3, logos, big numeric stats, hero titles
- Body/Paragraphs: Inter (Google Fonts)
  - Fallbacks: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif
  - Usage: Paragraphs, captions, labels, buttons

Suggested weights
- Orbitron: 600–800 for striking display
- Inter: 400 (body), 600–700 (buttons/labels)

## Accessibility
- Maintain high contrast: white text (#FFFFFF) on black (#000000)
- When using colored text, place on black or very dark backgrounds; avoid thin cyan-on-white
- Minimum contrast ratio target: 4.5:1 for body text

## Usage Guidance (Social Media)
- Backgrounds: solid black (#000000) with subtle grid or radial blue glows at 6% opacity
- CTAs/Buttons/Badges: primary gradient from #00A8FF to #00E5FF, text in black or very dark gray
- Active States/Highlights: use #00A8FF overlays at 10–25% opacity
- Underlines/Progress Bars: horizontal gradient from #00A8FF to #00E5FF
- Dividers/Containers: 1px border rgba(0,168,255,0.30–0.40) + soft glow
- Icons/Accents: white primary; hover or active in #00E5FF

## Quick Tokens (for reference)
- --background: #000000
- --foreground: #FFFFFF
- --glow-blue / primary: #00A8FF
- --glow-cyan / secondary: #00E5FF
- --neon-accent: #0066FF

## Examples
- Button (light-on-dark):
  - Background: gradient (#00A8FF → #00E5FF)
  - Text: #000000
  - Shadow: 0 0 24px rgba(0,168,255,0.30)
- Card:
  - Background: #000000 (95–98% opaque if overlayed)
  - Border: 1px solid rgba(0,168,255,0.35)
  - Shadow: 0 2px 42px rgba(0,229,255,0.12)
- Headline:
  - Font: Orbitron 700–800, all-caps optional
  - Color: gradient-filled text (#00A8FF → #00E5FF) when large; else #FFFFFF

## File Delivery Notes
- Provide exported assets for dark backgrounds; avoid embedded white backgrounds
- Keep gradients and glow layers editable in source files (PSD/AI/FIG)
- Use color styles in design tools named: Primary, Secondary, Accent, Background, Foreground

